## My request for Codex:
Act as senior full-stack engineer. Build the **Smart Notifications System** for DIABETLIYIM.

## üîî GOAL
Create an internal notifications system that connects doctors and patients based on medical events (prescriptions, labs, daily records, comments).

---

## üß¨ Backend Requirements (Notifications)

### üìå Create Model: Notification
```js
{
  user: ObjectId(ref User), // patient or doctor who receives the notification
  sender: ObjectId(ref User), // who triggered it (optional)
  type: String, // record_high, prescription_new, lab_request, lab_result, comment
  message: String,
  link: String, // optional link to open target page
  read: Boolean,
  createdAt: Date,
}

üìç Trigger notifications on events:
Event	Receiver	Type
Patient record is critical	Doctor	record_high
Doctor creates prescription	Patient	prescription_new
Doctor requests lab	Patient	lab_request
Patient uploads lab result	Doctor	lab_result
Doctor writes comment	Patient	comment

üìå API Endpoints
Method	Endpoint	Role	Result
GET	/api/notifications	logged user	list user notifications
PATCH	/api/notifications/read/:id	logged user	mark as read
PATCH	/api/notifications/read-all	logged user	mark all as read
DELETE	/api/notifications/:id	logged user	delete notification

üñ• Front-End Requirements
üîî Notification UI (Doctor & Patient)
Top bar icon üîî

Badge shows number of unread

Dropdown panel:

Show latest notifications (scrollable)

Each notification clickable ‚Üí redirect via link

Mark all as read

Delete notification

üé® Styles Needed
Badge color: #e11d48 (red)

Unread highlight background: #fff7f7

Hover effect: #e6fffa

üåç i18n Keys
ini
ŸÜÿ≥ÿÆ ÿßŸÑŸÉŸàÿØ
notifications.title = "Notifications"
notifications.mark_all = "Mark all as read"
notifications.no_notifications = "No notifications"
notifications.new_prescription = "New Prescription"
notifications.lab_request = "Lab Test Requested"
notifications.lab_result = "Lab Result Uploaded"
notifications.record_high = "Critical Glucose Level!"
notifications.comment = "New Comment from Doctor"
‚úî Deliverables
Notification backend model + triggers

Notification API

Frontend badge + dropdown

Link navigation behavior

i18n multilingual support
